commit.title: [ci] [gitlab] Remove Windows jobs.
commit.message:
[ci] [gitlab] Remove Windows jobs.

cc #7171, cc #7428 , closes #8622 , closes #9213 , closes #9401

Our windows worker setup has been problematic since day 1, and it is
creating frequent failures and other problems that cannot be publicly
disclosed.

IMSO this situation is not acceptable, the time has come to remove
them from our main CI infrastructure and have the Windows maintainers
implement the workflow in Azure / Travis.
